In this article, President Joe Biden speaks at a private residence in Los Gatos, California. He reflects on his first term as president and discusses his goals for the future. He emphasizes the importance of unity and restoring the soul of the nation. Biden also discusses his accomplishments, such as creating jobs and rebuilding relationships with international allies. He addresses issues such as gun control and women's reproductive rights, expressing his desire to implement policies that reflect the majority of Americans' views. Overall, Biden is optimistic about the future and believes that by working together, the country can achieve progress and overcome challenges.